<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home page</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-LN+7fdVzj6u52u30Kp6M/trliBMCMKTyK833zpbD+pXdCLuTusPj697FH4R/5mcr" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ndDqU0Gzau9qJ1lfW4pNLlhNTkCfHzAVBReH9diLvGRem5+R9g2FzA8ZGN954O5Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
</head>
<body class="text-center">
    <nav class="navbar" style="background-color: #e3f2fd;" data-bs-theme="light">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <img src="/images/logo.png" class="w-[15rem]" alt="logo">
            <span class="navbar-text">
                  <a class="navbar-brand text-black" href="/">Home</a>
                  <a class="navbar-brand text-black" href="/leader">LeaderBoard</a>
                  <a class="navbar-brand text-black" href="/question">Question</a>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
      </nav>
    <div class="bg-[url(/images/home_back.jpg)] bg-size-[100%_100%] bg-center w-[100vw] h-[100%] flex flex-col items-center text-left">
        <div class="backdrop-blur-md">
            <h1 class="text-center text-[10rem]">Trivia</h1>
            <h2 class="text-center text-[10rem]">To tinker with your brain</h2>
            <div class="w-[100vw] p-5">
                <h3>🧠 Welcome to the Trivia Arena – Where Curiosity Meets Competition! 🎉</h3>
                <p>Think you've got what it takes to outsmart the world? Step into the ultimate brainy battleground where every 6 hours a brand-new trivia question drops — and it's your moment to shine!

                Every question is a chance to flex those mental muscles. From mind-bending facts to fun pop culture nuggets, we’ll test your wit, memory, and maybe even your guessing skills (hey, we won’t judge!).</p>
            </div>
            <div  class="w-[100vw] p-5">
                <h3>⏰ How It Works:</h3>
                <p><ol>
                    <li>A fresh trivia question is unlocked every 6 hours. Morning, afternoon, night – there’s always something brewing.</li>
                    <li>You get one shot to answer, so make it count!</li>
                    <li>The faster and more accurately you answer, the more points you rack up.</li>
                    <li>No pressure... okay, maybe just a little.</li>
                    </ol></p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-[100vw] p-5">
                <h3>🌍 Climb the Global Leaderboard</h3>
                <p>This isn’t just for bragging rights (though we love those). Based on your performance, you’ll climb (or tumble😬) the worldwide leaderboard.
                    See how you stack up against friends, foes, and trivia buffs from every corner of the globe.
                    
                    Whether you're a late-night genius, a morning brainiac, or just love a good challenge, there’s always a chance to make your mark.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-[100vw] p-5">
                <h3>🔥 Why Join the Fun?</h3>
                <p><ol>
                    <li>Challenge yourself regularly</li>
                    <li>Discover weird and wonderful facts</li>
                    <li>Compete with trivia lovers across continents</li>
                    <li>Earn a spot among the trivia elite</li>
                    </ol></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>